========
Unity2048
========
http://www.iverv.com/2014/04/unity2048.html
http://www.iverv.com/2017/08/unity2048-2017.html

**Unity2048** is an unity-editor-based version of 2048_.

.. _2048: http://gabrielecirulli.github.io/2048/
.. _term2048: https://travis-ci.org/bfontaine/term2048

Contributions
-------------

v0.1.0, 2014-04-18 -- Initial release @verv
v0.2.0, 2017-08-01 -- Change main system, add cell moving/popin animation. @verv
v0.3.0, 2017-08-16 -- Add dynamic board and cell size. @verv
v0.3.1, 2017-08-15 -- Fixed animation bug. @verv
v0.4.0, 2017-08-17 -- Add key records and back action. @verv
